                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sweinfürt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                        Weigel <expan>Gras<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> nicht anheim ist. Doch so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hawsfr<ex>awen</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt etc. <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        die <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Sweinfürt <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>, ob
                        das <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>, sein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> auch
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>, als wir das den <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Sweinfurt <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> auch
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dienst etc.</ab>
